# Dashboard Layout Standards

## Zoom Formula (NEVER change)
zoom = Math.min(innerWidth/1608, innerHeight/900, 1)
Safe restore commit for zoom fix: 759b1c0

## Priority Alerts — Special Warning
The Priority Alerts section has caused multi-hour regressions. Rules:
- Never change the grid column count
- Never add scrollbars to the section
- Only add new cards — never modify existing ones unless explicitly approved
- Always verify Conversion Rate panel below is untouched after any change
- Never fill or remove empty placeholder slots

## Layout Rules
- Always fix UI issues globally across entire codebase, never spot-fix one instance
- Never let tab bars or meta rows wrap — shrink font, reduce gap, widen container
- Column widths in fixed px not %
- Full page edge-to-edge
